      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "Splitting was requested in other comment. \n\nI  don't see any reason to put links in source code to unofficial web source/documents. RFC 3986 has many rules and split this regex to each rule required a lot of effort. Tests confirmed that is correct and explain results of regex matching. \n\nCan I mark it as resolved ?",
